James Donald STRINGER, Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 13013. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. April 21, 1950. Rehearing Denied May 24,1950. W. G. Lagerquist, Jr., San Antonio, Tex., for appellant. Henry W. Moursund, U. S. Atty., San Antonio, Tex., Joel W. Westbrook, Asst. U. S. Atty., San Antonio,. Tex., for ap-pellee.

Before HOLMES, WALLER, and-BORAH, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.
